Installing
----------

      Sample Bank Editor requires the easylife extension (Also on aminet) to
      run inside AMOS. The compiled version requires only the mathtrans
      library.


Running
-------

      AMOS:

      Load AMOS. Load The Program. Press F1


      Compiled:

      Type "run SampleBankEditor" on the command line, or create an icon, and
      run it from the workbench.


Using The Program
-----------------

      Press return to close the about requester, then press the HELP key, and
      click on "Using Help", then "Getting Started".


Distribution
------------

      This program is freeware. Distribute it to anyone, but:

             - Pass on the complete archive.

             - Pass on the EasyLife archive as it won't work in AMOS
               without it.

             - Do not distribute modified copies.


